20:38.750 --> 20:42.250
Buddy, it is almost 1:00 in the morning,
and we have to be at work at 5:00.

20:42.333 --> 20:45.250
I know, but how often do we do this?

20:45.333 --> 20:47.000
You're absolutely right.
Come on.

20:48.041 --> 20:49.959
Do you have any 2's?

20:50.041 --> 20:52.625
Ah, no. Go fish, please.

20:52.709 --> 20:55.125
